- Check `success` first. If `false`, inspect `error.name`, `error.value`, and `error.traceback` before retrying.
- Local workspace files are not visible inside the E2B sandbox unless explicitly uploaded. If code needs a local file, pass it through `uploadFiles` and reference the `sandboxPath` inside the code.
- `uploadFiles.localPath` must point to a file under the configured workspace root. Relative paths are resolved from that root.
- If `uploadFiles.sandboxPath` is omitted, the file is uploaded under `/home/user/workspace/` preserving the relative local path.
